the precedent that you'd be setting?

04:30.021 --> 04:31.898
<i>- I 'd have to solicit the city council...
- Don't yell at me.</i>

04:32.023 --> 04:33.233
<i>...to even get funding to retain a lawyer.</i>

04:33.358 --> 04:34.359
You know what?

04:34.443 --> 04:37.779
