year for us, Sparkles.

06:11.623 --> 06:14.042
COSMO: <i>We'll just go away forever.</i>
TIMMY: <i>Why?</i>

06:14.125 --> 06:16.044
- WAN <i>DA: That's what the rulebook says.
-(CH UCKLES)</i>

06:17.295 --> 06:18.296
