06:18.380 --> 06:20.966
Oh, wow. Bit of a line here.

06:22.634 --> 06:23.718
Oh, it'll move quickly.

06:23.802 --> 06:26.096
We just drop-and-go.
They've got it down to a science.

06:26.179 --> 06:27.472
JOSH: Water, water, water.

06:27.973 --> 06:29.099
We don't go in?

06:29.182 --> 06:32.018
