12:35.715 --> 12:36.799
Fuck.

12:37.800 --> 12:39.052
Hey, hey. Hey, hey-

12:39.552 --> 12:41.054
Sorry. It's just...

12:42.055 --> 12:44.057
Fuck. I'm sorry.

12:46.184 --> 12:49.562
It's just, all this traveling,
I feel like I'm missing out on so much.

12:49.854 --> 12:51.230
