12:53.399 --> 12:55.193
Sorry. Sorry, sorry.

13:00.323 --> 13:02.700
Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey-

13:08.873 --> 13:10.249
No,no,no,no,no.

13:10.500 --> 13:12.210
