or I'm getting an attorney.

42:02.230 --> 42:04.857
- Okay, we're not there yet, Mrs Klein.
- I'm there.

42:04.941 --> 42:06.693
God. Attorneys? Really? Is that necessary?

42:06.859 --> 42:10.238
Actually, in my graduate thesis,
I coined the term "helicopter parent."

42:10.863 --> 42:13.950
But these gems, they're fucking kamikazes.

42:14.534 --> 42:15.535
And I'm not kidding.

42:15.618 --> 42:18.788
No one takes responsibility for anything,
and Chloe's involved.

42:18.913 --> 42:20.915
MADELINE: ...not to mention
her health and well-being.

42:21.124 --> 42:25.628
I mean, if I had a dime for every boy
that I tried to kiss when I was six years old,

42:26.254 --> 42:28.131
I mean, I can't even tell you,
there were so many.

42:28.214 --> 42:29.966
They're children, for Christ's sakes.

42:30.091 --> 42:32.802
They're supposed to be
doing things like kissing each other.

42:36.389 --> 42:37.432
Jane?

42:39.267 --> 42:40.727
What's wrong, honey?

42:40.935 --> 42:41.978
(SOBBING)

42:42.812 --> 42:43.813
You Okay?

42:46.232 --> 42:47.442
I'm sorry, I just...

42:49.652 --> 42:51.654
MADELINE: Honey. It's okay.

42:52.488 --> 42:55.742
They're just kids. By this time tomorrow
it will all have blown over.

42:57.785 --> 42:58.953
Come on.

42:59.954 --> 43:02.081
(SOFT MUSIC PLAYING)

43:09.630 --> 43:11.340
How can you not wanna make up
on this song?

43:11.424 --> 43:12.425
Come on!

43:12.508 --> 43:14.969
Make up, yes, not make out, silly.

43:16.345 --> 43:20.266
It's what you guys do when you get mad
at each other, big hug, kiss, bang!

43:20.349 --> 43:21.768
And everything's better again.

43:21.851 --> 43:25.021
- But it's different with married people.
- Why?

43:25.271 --> 43:27.690
I don't know. ltjust is. Don't start with me.

43:40.536 --> 43:42.330
This is a beautiful song, honey.

43:55.384 --> 43:57.512
(SKYPE TONE CHIMING)

44:02.141 --> 44:03.351
Hey, baby.

44:04.977 --> 44:07.230
- PERRY: Hey, Sparkles.
- I thought it was like midnight there.

44:07.313 --> 44:08.856
<i>Yeah, well, I can't sleep.</i>

44:09.524 --> 44:10.858
<i>Jet lag.</i>

44:11.651 --> 44:12.693
Right.

44:15.988 --> 44:17.365
<i>Is that the bathrobe I bought you?</i>

44:17.865 --> 44:18.908
Mmm-hmm.

44:19.158 --> 44:20.326
<i>- It is.
- Ah...</i>

44:21.577 --> 44:24.497
Thank you for the flowers. They're beautiful.

44:29.252 --> 44:30.419
<i>I miss you.</i>

44:30.878 --> 44:33.089
Yeah. Miss you, too.

44:34.549 --> 44:36.050
And the boys miss you.

44:37.385 --> 44:38.928
<i>So how was their second day?</i>

44:41.222 --> 44:42.265
It was fine.

44:43.391 --> 44:44.433
(CHUCKLES)

44:49.689 --> 44:51.274
<i>Will you do me a favor?</i>

44:56.612 --> 44:57.697
What?

44:57.780 --> 44:59.949
<i>Would you take that beautiful robe off
for a second?</i>

45:00.700 --> 45:01.742
(CHUCKLES)

45:03.202 --> 45:05.288
