45:05.788 --> 45:08.082
<i>Yeah, well, I have to help myself go to sleep.</i>

45:09.542 --> 45:11.586
<i>I need you to help me help myself.</i>

45:12.128 --> 45:13.296
Do I now?

45:15.256 --> 45:17.884
<i>Let me just a look at
my gorgeous wife for a second.</i>

45:19.927 --> 45:20.970
<i>Ten seconds.</i>

45:23.139 --> 45:24.390
I'll give you five.

45:25.308 --> 45:26.934
<i>Well, make it a nice five.</i>

45:46.329 --> 45:47.413
(CLEARS THROAT)

45:48.331 --> 45:50.583
Okay. That's enough, naughty boy.

45:52.835 --> 45:54.837
