if you want more.

45:58.090 --> 45:59.133
<i>Come closer.</i>

46:07.016 --> 46:08.100
<i>I love you.</i>

46:13.022 --> 46:14.815
Take her out of school
if you're that concerned.

46:15.983 --> 46:18.694
She's the one that has to leave?
She didn't do anything...

46:18.819 --> 46:22.531
I just don't think legal action is the answer.
All right?

46:23.366 --> 46:25.701
Let's see how it goes.
I'm guessing it'll all sort itself out.

46:25.826 --> 46:28.120
- I do not feel supported here.
-(SIGHS)

46:29.205 --> 46:30.289
Well.

46:31.457 --> 46:33.376
I don't suppose
I could argue with your feelings.

46:46.222 --> 46:47.306
(CHUCKLES)

46:47.390 --> 46:49.392
JANE: Ziggy, why are you awake?

46:50.476 --> 46:52.353
