(SIGHS)

47:54.457 --> 47:56.584
Pickles and mustard.

47:57.752 --> 47:59.045
I'm not pregnant.

48:00.546 --> 48:05.885
You know, if that day ever comes,
the one you alluded to earlier...

48:06.052 --> 48:07.094
Hmm.

48:07.219 --> 48:09.472
The day I decide to have sex? That day?

48:10.639 --> 48:11.932
Yes, that one.

48:13.309 --> 48:14.935
Can we talk about it first?

48:17.313 --> 48:18.439
Sure.

48:19.273 --> 48:22.568
'Cause I actually think I could be helpful.

48:24.445 --> 48:25.488
Okay.

48:26.781 --> 48:28.657
I have a lot of girlfriends, as you know.

48:28.991 --> 48:33.954
