to beat him up.

48:51.055 --> 48:52.139
Oh...

48:52.348 --> 48:53.641
Of course not.

48:57.812 --> 49:00.272
He wanted me to get you
to back off Bonnie a little bit,

49:00.356 --> 49:02.358
it led to a discussion, and...

49:02.483 --> 49:04.360
I never threatened to beat him up.

49:05.611 --> 49:08.614
I did let him know
I wouldn't be intimidated by him,

49:08.697 --> 49:10.491
which, I think, was his intent.

49:11.450 --> 49:12.993
So how did you two leave it?

49:13.994 --> 49:15.037
We left it...

49:16.330 --> 49:18.541
He's got Bonnie's back and I've got yours.

49:21.544 --> 49:22.628
My He-Man.

49:23.129 --> 49:24.130
Oh, come on.

49:24.213 --> 49:26.382
(LAUGHING)

49:29.885 --> 49:31.220
Can I just say one thing?

49:32.221 --> 49:34.014
You never leave it at one thing.

49:36.892 --> 49:38.227
You're the one, okay?

49:42.148 --> 49:43.399
You're my only one.

49:58.080 --> 50:00.249
